Sentencas: Tubular NiO/YSZ anode-supports of solid oxide fuel cells were prepared successfully by gelcasting process.
Titulo: Gelcasting of NiO/YSZ Tubular Anode-Supports for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Based on an investigation of the rheological behaviors of the ceramic particle suspensions for gelcasting, stable NiO/YSZ aqueous slurry with optimal monomer, dispersant, and solid loading is defined.
Titulo: Gelcasting of NiO/YSZ Tubular Anode-Supports for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The results show that the addition of pore formers influences not only the viscosity of suspensions but also the gelation rate of the gelcasting systems.
Titulo: Gelcasting of NiO/YSZ Tubular Anode-Supports for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Scanning electron microscope reveals that the microstructure of the green body is homogeneous and compact without apparent agglomerate or pores.
Titulo: Gelcasting of NiO/YSZ Tubular Anode-Supports for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
